  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Publish What You Pay &#x2013; UK Coordinator costs 2014</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Campaign for a global standard of oil, gas and mining payment transparency and work to transform transparency into government and industry accountability.  The EU is expected to finalize its Directives in the first half of 2013, after which PWYP UK will focus its efforts on ensuring timely and effective transposition into domestic law, including adequate domestic guidance for reporting companies, provision for making the data accessible and government monitoring; defending the rules against industry opposition; developing strategies to make use of the data, once available.</narrative>
  </description>
